{
  "stem": "7455.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was reading the paper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He didn't look up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I poured beer in a glass for him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the rest I left on the night table near him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I came into the kitchen to Mrs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Schubert, ?] and I told her what happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said, dear, God, how long are you going to punish us?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How long are we going to suffer?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES] And [PAUSES] after, in the afternoon, I went home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When Mr.-- Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was away, we watched.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I brought the news.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people came to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The next-- after a few days, we heard rumors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We heard the rumors that there's going to be a roundup-- [? aktion, ?] they call it-- a roundup of Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We already knowing what happened, the killing and the shooting, from the previous roundup.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We already knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sitting in our cellar there, we did not know if it's safe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, again, we thought, are we going to go up there?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we thought we might not be lucky this time, because they're going to go have a more thorough search.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we thought, perhaps we'll go into the woods, because the ghetto was not created then.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we are free to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At night, we'll go to the woods and wait in the woods.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What was-- my father's sister, Rachel, went to the woods with her children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was dealing, like pedaling goods and things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she dealt with farmers, so she knew some.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She went to a farm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she had some-- saved some materials that she had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She figured, maybe they're going to hide our-- find a hiding place for her and the children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the farmer had a small place with children that he said they wouldn't be safe.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
